OL,3,CMan and woman found dead in Aberavon
OL,4,Chouse after police force entry
OL,6,FA man and a woman were found dead in a
OL,7,Fliving room in Aberavon after police
OL,8,Fforced entry into a house.
OL,10,FOfficers had been investigating a
OL,11,Fsuspected breach of a bail condition.
OL,13,FAn inquest was opened into the deaths
OL,14,Fof Roxanne Louvain Williams and Craig
OL,15,FPhillip Hall at Swansea's Guildhall on
OL,16,FTuesday, 15 February, 2024.
OL,18,FIt heard that Mr Hall, 40, was on tag
OL,19,Fand subject to a bail condition
OL,20,Fregarding his place of residence in
OL,21,FBriton Ferry.
