OL,3,CMan and woman found dead in Aberavon
OL,4,Chouse after police force entry
OL,6,FHe wasn't there, and police were
OL,7,Fdirected to the address of 34-year-old
OL,8,FMiss Williams, his ex-partner, in Port
OL,9,FTalbot, where he was believed to be
OL,10,Fstaying.
OL,12,FOn February 5, police attended her
OL,13,Fproperty at Rhodes Avenue, Aberavon,
OL,14,Fwhere they forcibly gained entry and
OL,15,Ffound two bodies in the living room.
OL,17,FCoroner's officer Sue Davies told the
OL,18,Fhearing, in a report, how officers
OL,19,Falso found prescribed drugs, some
OL,20,Funknown tablets, and white powder on
OL,21,Fthe premises.
