OL,4,Chouse after police force entry
OL,6,FA Home Office forensic post-mortem
OL,7,Fexamination found no signs of trauma
OL,8,Ffor either person with the cause of
OL,9,Ftheir deaths yet to be ascertained.
OL,11,FActing senior coroner Colin Phillips
OL,12,Fhas adjourned the inquests until 24
OL,13,FJuly at 10.30 am.
